originalText.text: Elena has walked our two hound dogs on two separate occasions. Both times went great. Elena was very communicative, sent us updates on the dogs like we requested and even shared a couple of pictures from the walk. Elena has been very responsible in her ways of handling the dogs and easy to communicate with along the way. I would definitely recommend her to anyone looking for a trusted pet sitter.

originalText.text:
I had the pleasure of hiring Elena’s Pet to take care of my four legged son and I couldn't be happier with the service provided.  Elena is not just a dog walker but a true pet lover. She was punctual, reliable, and always greeted my four legged son with a warm smile.

What sets Elena apart is her genuine care and attention to detail. She always provides updates after each walk, letting me know how Raddie did and if there were any special moments during the walk.

I highly recommend Elena to anyone in need of a reliable and caring dog walker. Thank you Elena, for your outstanding service.

originalText.text: My wife and I have been using Elena’s cat sitting services for two years now, and she never disappoints. She’s dependable, professional, and maintains consistent contact with us while we’re out of town. We used to worry about ensuring our cats were cared for while we traveled, but now we rest easy knowing we have such a reliable sitter. And most importantly, our cats have grown quite fond of her! If you’re in the area and need a cat sitter, I highly recommend Elena.

originalText.text: Elena is wonderful!! She took care of our 2 dogs (including our special needs diabetic dog who requires insulin shots) during a family vacation. She was so attentive to them, sent daily pictures and updates. They love her and are so happy to see her when she comes by for walks! I am extremely protective of my dog babies but when they are in her care I know they are in excellent hands. Her colleague Taj is also wonderful and great with the dogs. If you are looking for a professional, reliable, trustworthy, loving pet sitter look no further then Elena!

originalText.text: Absolutely recommend Elena’s pets! Elena was so flexible and communicative when arranging my dog Ed’s walks. She is very reliable and my dog took to her immediately (which says a lot because he can be very particular). My dog has some frustration-based reactivity, and I was happy to learn Elena had experience with this. She managed this without issues and I feel very secure having Ed in her care. Will 100% keep using her services!
